			                <p style="color: black;"><b>Once you click "Reserve" you AGREE to our Terms and Conditions</b></p>
                            <p style="color: black;">1. Reservation Process: The online hotel reservation process allows you to reserve a room or suite at the selected hotel. The reservation will be confirmed by the admin.
                            </p>
                            <p style="color: black;">2. Personal Information: By making a reservation, you agree to provide accurate and complete personal information, including your name, address, and payment information. The hotel reserves the right to request additional identification or payment verification on-site.
