                            <p style="color: black;">6. These terms and conditions constitute the entire agreement between the clients and the hotel only. This conditions overrule all prior agreements or misunderstandings made by any party (ex: staff, manager, clients, admin, etc.) whether written or oral.</p>
		                </div>
	                </div>
